We'll be checking in with the 2016 cohort periodically, and can't wait to
see what they accomplish over the course of their 15month grants!
How to get involved
Become an IDEAS volunteer!
ItE2s all about collaboration. When passionate individuals pool thei
r
skills, knowledge, and resources, we can tackle just about anything. IDEAS
teams have developed solutions to some of societyE2s most difficult 
problems
with the help of dedicated volunteers like you.

Among the most valuable resources that you can share are skills, knowledge,
and experience. Reach out to us if you would like to serve as a mentor,
reviewer, or event volunteer.

